"The user starts with View 1 (Overview) to understand metric distributions across customer statuses. Selecting specific status groups filters Views 2-4. In View 3 (Exploration), ratio sliders create dynamic segments that propagate to Views 4-6. View 4's parallel coordinates reveal demographic patterns, while Views 5-6 (Insights) highlight extreme cases and trends. The pipeline enables progressive refinement from general patterns to specific actionable insights."